+//! Benchmarks for Bayesian Online Change-Point Detection (BOCPD).
+//!
+//! Performance budgets:
+//! - Single observation update: **< 50μs**
+//! - Feature vector compute (1KB): **< 100μs**
+//! - Batch 100 panes update: **< 5ms**
+//! - Snapshot serialization: **< 500μs**
