+//! Performance budgets:
+//! - Snapshot capture (10 panes): **< 5ms**
+//! - Snapshot capture (50 panes): **< 20ms**
+//! - State hash computation: **< 100us**
+//! - Checkpoint save to SQLite: **< 10ms**
+//! - Checkpoint load from SQLite: **< 5ms**
